<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/health-and-safety-executive> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Health and Safety Executive (HSE) is Britain’s national regulator for workplace health and safety. It prevents work-related death, injury and ill health. HSE is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Work and Pensions ."@en .
